fields.name: IPAddressType
fields.description: The IP address type of this frontend configuration. If omitted the default value is IPv4.

fields.name: LoadBalancerBackendAddressPoolId
fields.description: The resource Id of the Load Balancer backend address pool that the VM instances of the node type are associated with. The format of the resource Id is '/subscriptions/<subscriptionId>/resourceGroups/<resourceGroupName>/providers/Microsoft.Network/loadBalancers/<loadBalancerName>/backendAddressPools/<backendAddressPoolName>'.

fields.name: LoadBalancerInboundNatPoolId
fields.description: The resource Id of the Load Balancer inbound NAT pool that the VM instances of the node type are associated with. The format of the resource Id is '/subscriptions/<subscriptionId>/resourceGroups/<resourceGroupName>/providers/Microsoft.Network/loadBalancers/<loadBalancerName>/inboundNatPools/<inboundNatPoolName>'.
